<a name="ih10-wb-ramps"></a>
<div class="problem-heading">IH-10 westbound: Possibly Provide a Dedicated Lane for the Ramp Connecting from IH-69</div>
<div class="textblock">
    <div>
        <div>This idea depends on which ramp has higher traffic volume, the ramp from IH-69 or the entrance ramp from McKee Street. If the IH-69 ramp has higher volume, an adjustment could be warranted.</div>

    </div>
    <div class="problem-solution">Possible Item for Improvement</div>
    <ul>
        <li>The exit from IH-69 to westbound IH-10 merges into the 3-lane IH-10 main lanes</li>
        <li>Just to the west, the entrance ramp from McKee Street has a dedicated lane</li>
    </ul>
    <div class="problem-solution">Potential Change</div>
    <ul>
        <li>If the ramp from IH-69 has higher traffic volume, then the ramp from IH-69 should have a dedicated entrance lane and the ramp from McKee should be merged into IH-10 without a dedicated lane</li>
    </ul>

</div>

